events.title: OFFICIAL IMEX PARTY
events.description: Together with EVINTRA, CIM - Conference & Incentive Management organises the official trade fair party of IMEX Frankfurt: CIMclubbing. This year, CIMclubbing @ imex will take place in the new Galeria Frankfurt restaurant. On the large roof terrace, with a view of the Frankfurt skyline, you can round off the first day of IMEX with dinner and drinks together with colleagues and customers. At a later hour, our DJ will invite you to the dance floor. Secure your tickets now!
